Windows:

Using VM VirtualBox:

** add description ***


Using Docker Desktop:

Install Docker Desktop for Windows:
https://hub.docker.com/editions/community/docker-ce-desktop-windows

Install VcXsrv:
https://sourceforge.net/projects/vcxsrv

After installing it, start XLaunch and click "Next" until you reach "Extra Settings". Once there, be sure to disable access control, otherwise the request from Docker will be rejected.

*** add screenshot ***

Clone the repository under "C:\Users\%USERNAME%\Documents\ControleVBC\":
https://github.com/lnls-sirius/vacuum-bbb-controller.git

Copy the VBC.bat file under vacuum-bbb-controller/software/docker/ and launch it.
